// Template for local signing config.
//
// Setup:
//   1. Copy this file:  cp Signing.xcconfig.example Signing.xcconfig
//   2. Fill in your Apple Developer team ID + Developer ID Application identity.
//   3. Run `xcodegen generate` and build.
//
// Signing.xcconfig is gitignored, so your team ID / name never get committed.
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID
CODE_SIGN_IDENTITY = Developer ID Application: YOUR NAME (YOUR_TEAM_ID)
